<body>
  <h1>ğŸ‚ Â¡Ayuda a Andrea a encontrar su pastel de cumpleaÃ±os!</h1>
  <div id="musicControl" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <button id="playMusicButton" style="font-size: 28px; background: none; color: #fff; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'American Typewriter', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;">â–¶ï¸</button>
    <span style="font-size: 18px; color: #fff; font-family: 'American Typewriter', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;">Activa la mÃºsica</span>
